main event: A sighting of an unidentified flying object (UFO) reported in Spotsylvania, Virginia, that appeared to move in a manner similar to a bird but without visible wings.
interesting points: The object was observed for approximately 10 minutes., Witnesses described the object as being the size of a small dog or house., It darted at high altitude in an erratic manner., The object's movement resembled that of a duck, but it lacked wings or propellers., The report indicates that the object left physical evidence and was part of multiple sightings in the area.
sighted object: an unidentified flying object resembling a bird
witness description: The witness was a traveling salesman who observed a bright light hovering above the highway.
